lead_paragraph: Peyton Manning was expected to be backup quarterback for the Denver Broncos in their regular season finale against the San Diego Chargers on Sunday after being listed as probable on Friday's injury report.

headline.print_headline: Manning Set for Backup Role in Regular Season Finale
